---
title: Mexican Style Tortilla Bake with Kidney Beans, Soured Cream and Cheese
description: This all-in-one dish is guaranteed to get a thumbs up from the whole family. Chef Lizzie has created a Mexican-style ‘lasagne’, using whole-wheat tortillas instead of sheets of pasta, filling each layer with a veg-packed tomato sauce and baking it until the cheesy topping is golden and bubbly. Serve up in the middle of your table along with all the toppings and dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-tortilla-bake-28ca90e9-f0641188.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/mexican-tortilla-bake-5b3f593530006c1c9f5cdd62-3b327793.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
